    "description": "<strong>迈克有麻烦了！ </strong>他的花园正在失去控制，需要你的帮助。 匹配物种、创造性地使用工具并连续使用令人难以置信的组合，尽可能地生存下去！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/500d182dd21a11c74a6982ddb03c641a.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/500d182dd21a11c74a6982ddb03c641a.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e54a6f4f171a8488e9479a6df7222c7d.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br>让您的游戏独一无二！ 每场比赛赚取种子，在您自己的私人温室中解锁新物种。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e6cb2cd4ac85b87f35d0c99992eb4546.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e6cb2cd4ac85b87f35d0c99992eb4546.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/8aec72cb1e4b31044399b795c9998945.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br>解锁不同的常见或疯狂的花园管理工具来控制你的董事会。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/f49aa43fbe8bac23f97d1e6943e290c8.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/f49aa43fbe8bac23f97d1e6943e290c8.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/a44046e6a7d2109828d3319f8af10971.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br>获胜的唯一方法就是成为名誉花园中的花园之王。 通过掌握你的策略并从不分享你的园艺技巧和技巧来击败你的朋友。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/579980f72a17e43f03e29bedfbaa5722.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/579980f72a17e43f03e29bedfbaa5722.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/579980f72a17e43f03e29bedfbaa5722.mp4?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/99d3f61f32d03777a23b9af7060b2960.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br><br>通过实践学习。完成所有微型任务，教您解锁独特植物的机制和系统。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e8b2502db72d4aa38b7bb0cba1edd5cf.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e8b2502db72d4aa38b7bb0cba1edd5cf.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
